videoSnippet.title: Supi Crushes Magnus Carlsen in 18 Moves!
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content and notifications https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Luis Paulo Supi vs Magnus Carlsen
Online match on chess.com (2020)
Scandinavian (centre counter) defence (B01)

1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Qxd5 3. Nf3 Bg4 4. Be2 Nc6 5. Nc3 Qd7 6. h3 Bxf3 7. Bxf3 O-O-O 8. O-O Nd4 9. a4 Kb8 10. Nb5 Nxf3+ 11. Qxf3 a6 12. c4 e5 13. d4 exd4 14. Bf4 axb5 15. axb5 Bd6 16. Ra2 Qf5 17. Rfa1 Kc8 18. Qc6
